#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.58"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.58:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.58:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sudattaanāthapiṇḍikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.58:0.3"
msgid "58. Sudattasutta"
msgstr "58. Sudatta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.58:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.64"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.58:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Bhojanaṃ, gahapati, dadamāno ariyasāvako paṭiggāhakānaṃ cattāri ṭhānāni "
"deti."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, when a noble disciple gives food, they give the recipients "
"four things."

msgctxt "an4.58:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.58:2.3"
msgid "Āyuṃ deti, vaṇṇaṃ deti, sukhaṃ deti, balaṃ deti."
msgstr "Long life, beauty, happiness, and strength."

msgctxt "an4.58:2.4"
msgid "Āyuṃ kho pana datvā āyussa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "Giving long life, they have long life as a god or human. …"

msgctxt "an4.58:2.5"
msgid ""
"Vaṇṇaṃ datvā … sukhaṃ datvā … balaṃ datvā balassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā "
"mānusassa vā."
msgstr "Giving beauty … happiness … strength …"

msgctxt "an4.58:2.6"
msgid ""
"Bhojanaṃ, gahapati, dadamāno ariyasāvako paṭiggāhakānaṃ imāni cattāri "
"ṭhānāni detīti."
msgstr ""
"When a noble disciple gives food, they give the recipients these four things."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.1"
msgid "Yo saññatānaṃ paradattabhojinaṃ,"
msgstr "Carefully giving food at the right time,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.2"
msgid "Kālena sakkacca dadāti bhojanaṃ;"
msgstr "to those who are restrained, eating only what others give,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.3"
msgid "Cattāri ṭhānāni anuppavecchati,"
msgstr "you provide them with four things:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:3.4"
msgid "Āyuñca vaṇṇañca sukhaṃ balañca."
msgstr "long life, beauty, happiness, and strength."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: vaṇṇadāyī → so āyudāyī baladāyī (bj, pts1) | āyudāyī baladāyī (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an4.58:4.1"
msgid "So āyudāyī vaṇṇadāyī,"
msgstr "A person who gives long life, beauty,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sukhaṃ balaṃ dado → sukhaṃ vaṇṇaṃ dado (bj, s1-3, km) | sukhavaṇṇadado (pts1) | sukhabaladado (mr)
msgctxt "an4.58:4.2"
msgid "sukhaṃ balaṃ dado naro;"
msgstr "happiness, and strength,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:4.3"
msgid "Dīghāyu yasavā hoti,"
msgstr "has long life and fame"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.58:4.4"
msgid "yattha yatthūpapajjatī”ti."
msgstr "wherever they’re reborn.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.58:4.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
